{"tid":1083179,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"★ g嬸金曲台之 Blue Jeans 藍戰士 (^_^)","createTime":"2019-03-29T12:23:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-03T03:13:49.000Z","uid":44730,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"1e0c6dbcfb0a9effaf4b6bc7b6f425abd3e12b09","tid":1083179,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T12:23:22.000Z","msg":"重開 <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/24/014534_12dce3cb521d639bb955ddb0f91a02e5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F24%2F014534_12dce3cb521d639bb955ddb0f91a02e5.png&h=feefedce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/kaoAPTVGgvM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FkaoAPTVGgvM&d=tn6C2tKLXSv13zRFu6un7W5pKsuoI6OgBDFn4N8w%2Bso%3D&h=4f3c22c7\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/kaoAPTVGgvM</a><br />\n<br />\n87年迎合大熱的樂隊潮流，請來Blue Jeans為《住家男人》重新編曲、合唱、彈奏，並配合1+3把鬈髮製造噱頭。他們簽了SONY/CBS，第一張EP《豈有此理》和林憶蓮的Remix EP在差不多同期推出。<br />\n<br />\n另外兩個版本<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/K_b13JchpOc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FK_b13JchpOc&d=tn6C2tKLXSv13zRFu6un7W5pKsuoI6OgBDFn4N8w%2Bso%3D&h=cc1f0954\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/K_b13JchpOc</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/J8an4grdwEA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FJ8an4grdwEA&d=tn6C2tKLXSv13zRFu6un7W5pKsuoI6OgBDFn4N8w%2Bso%3D&h=4a440ec3\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/J8an4grdwEA</a>"},{"pid":"2e71f89f224b570655738f09f5ae2b19e23c7927","tid":1083179,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T12:24:14.000Z","msg":"封面用繪畫表現樂隊三位成員，化身三劍俠，劍是結他，大碟主打歌 : 人生酒庫、藍戰士、浪漫的年頭<br />\n<br />\n港台廣播劇＜神探福爾摩＞主題曲<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/sU4Nv2ntvbM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FsU4Nv2ntvbM&d=tn6C2tKLXSv13zRFu6un7W5pKsuoI6OgBDFn4N8w%2Bso%3D&h=39dd7f65\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/sU4Nv2ntvbM</a>"},{"pid":"993d07e916dd45e18ae055b5579a0baded223527","tid":1083179,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T12:24:41.000Z","msg":"三人曾為Chyna樂隊成員，組成＜藍戰士＞後以＜豈有此理＞ <a href=\"https://bit.ly/2TDjs5D\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2TDjs5D&d=tn6C2tKLXSv13zRFu6un7W5pKsuoI6OgBDFn4N8w%2Bso%3D&h=d8216728\" target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2TDjs5D</a> 獲流行歌曲創作大賽冠軍而打響名堂，除三人齊流長髮的形象十分突出外，三人都有作曲和演奏，而單立文也曾參與填詞，Blue Jeans可說是八十年代中後期樂隊熱潮中的實力派樂隊，代表作有＜人生酒庫＞、＜人到無求＞、＜午夜情人＞、＜下雨天＞、＜住家男人＞等。<br />\n<br />\n組成3年後，於90年解散，2004年一度加入新成員重組，但名氣已大不如前。"},{"pid":"1787097da1bdf20133079b9604829bdf13608237","tid":1083179,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T12:25:42.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/HKLvp9YoP9g\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FHKLvp9YoP9g&d=tn6C2tKLXSv13zRFu6un7W5pKsuoI6OgBDFn4N8w%2Bso%3D&h=6c8cb3b9\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/HKLvp9YoP9g</a><br />\n<br />\n原作 Reflections of My Life 是60年代搖滾，可當作向經典致敬，以及樂隊戰士堅持音樂理想的心志。"},{"pid":"3351ccfc7f5d5811c44ccb36f9e68e2eac2151f0","tid":1083179,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T12:26:02.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/51cphOj4Gdk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F51cphOj4Gdk&d=tn6C2tKLXSv13zRFu6un7W5pKsuoI6OgBDFn4N8w%2Bso%3D&h=8ef0de2b\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/51cphOj4Gdk</a><br />\n<br />\n88年中帶來大碟，正改中文名藍戰士，並有首歌就叫《藍戰士》，另一主打是《人生酒庫》，以喝酒比喻人生有苦有甜，要嘗過才知，勇敢 take the good times and the bad times，相當有意思的歌詞。MV請來林志美、陳少偉、蔣志光、王利名、吳國敬、許志安、文佩玲客串， 他們先後都試過風光和黯淡，亦很貼題。"},{"pid":"227705915987faab06d6a02408cbcc98c90f3fda","tid":1083179,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T12:26:37.000Z","msg":"留住爆炸頭嘅黃良昇，與妻育有一子一女，其中囡囡已經21歲(2017)，長得亭亭玉立，問到昇哥會唔會介紹囡囡入行，做吓model嗰啲，昇哥話：「個女冇提過想入行或做模特兒，個女鍾意做咩就做咩，冇所謂。」至於已經26歲(2017) 嘅長子，就係一個愛動物人士，養好多動物，而家喺一間非牟利嘅寵物領養及寄養中心工作。<br />\n<br />\n昇哥話仔女都鍾意意樂，但自己唔敢親自教，怕有壓力，不過，昇哥搵朋友教佢對仔女時，就到朋友話有壓力，昇哥仲話：「試過教個仔打鼓，但隔籬屋話『我瞓緊覺，唔好意思，可唔可以細聲啲？』咁終於又冇玩到。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20170309/large/1489072640_f97d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170309%2Flarge%2F1489072640_f97d.jpg&h=30e26e08&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20170309/large/1489072643_c100.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170309%2Flarge%2F1489072643_c100.jpg&h=5aa57e85&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"22ae8a2e21a60bfe5ac8402b86cbaae52c6a7732","tid":1083179,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T12:27:35.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/hEjCSvvPahM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FhEjCSvvPahM&d=tn6C2tKLXSv13zRFu6un7W5pKsuoI6OgBDFn4N8w%2Bso%3D&h=66a8c3b3\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/hEjCSvvPahM</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/YTvsDUtAe_4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FYTvsDUtAe_4&d=tn6C2tKLXSv13zRFu6un7W5pKsuoI6OgBDFn4N8w%2Bso%3D&h=1a2ef149\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/YTvsDUtAe_4</a><br />\n<br />\n在1988上映的《金裝大酒店》客串及《夢過界》，亦有張學友同王祖賢主演。"},{"pid":"bb643bdccad2542a6311991197825a7bfafe16b9","tid":1083179,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T13:12:53.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/qvXv5soQ9Vk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FqvXv5soQ9Vk&d=tn6C2tKLXSv13zRFu6un7W5pKsuoI6OgBDFn4N8w%2Bso%3D&h=af3330a2\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/qvXv5soQ9Vk</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Hg7gf2kv_Po\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FHg7gf2kv_Po&d=tn6C2tKLXSv13zRFu6un7W5pKsuoI6OgBDFn4N8w%2Bso%3D&h=8024f723\" target=\"_blank\">h